https://github.com/noahstokes/sandy-relief

=============================

This is a simple splash page that you can put on your website to redirect visitors to donate to the Red Cross to help support surivivors of Sandy. This is licensed under the MIT and GPL licenses. 

See the original: http://yaronschoen.com

Usage is simple:

1) Edit the index.html to point to your homepage for the 'Contine to the site' link. 

2) Adjust the path to the style.css (if you place it somewhere other than your root).

3) Upload to your server.

4) Donate yourself.

